    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个神秘的存在被关在了你父亲的研究中心里。为了拯救你身患绝症的女儿，你在绝望之中对这个可怕的野兽宣誓效忠。与那个生物共生，让它自由，它就会答应你治好女儿。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以一名不起眼的科学家身份在研究设施里行动。通过与同事交谈，与环境互动以收集信息并释放野兽。变身成野兽形态穿过通风管道，并与实验室内的士兵和其他生物血战，杀出一条路来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一名心碎的父亲被迫做出了绝望与牺牲之举。释放内心的野兽，用尽一切方法拯救你的女儿。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只有噩梦才能消除另一场噩梦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>核心玩法：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>双面性</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086670/extras/b0630b28d33cbb9115945eebf244dc81.poster.avif?t=1765469793\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086670/extras/b0630b28d33cbb9115945eebf244dc81.webm?t=1765469793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086670/extras/b0630b28d33cbb9115945eebf244dc81.mp4?t=1765469793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人类与野兽两种角色——制定策略选择合适的形态面对不同的情况。使用两种形态，用最务实的方式通过关卡。两种形态都有着深层含义，并会对剧情发展造成深远影响。你化身野兽时杀掉的人将会影响故事的结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>血腥的战斗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086670/extras/dc71b68f7ecc474551b159e38579b821.poster.avif?t=1765469793\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086670/extras/dc71b68f7ecc474551b159e38579b821.webm?t=1765469793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086670/extras/dc71b68f7ecc474551b159e38579b821.mp4?t=1765469793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >脆弱迟钝的人类形态会与强大敏捷的野兽形态形成鲜明的对比。撕碎挡路的士兵。杀害无辜之人会给予你被动强化，并解锁处决技能……但这种行为伴随着沉重的代价。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>情感化叙事</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086670/extras/be8f3da168dc3518635643186dd1ea67.poster.avif?t=1765469793\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086670/extras/be8f3da168dc3518635643186dd1ea67.webm?t=1765469793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086670/extras/be8f3da168dc3518635643186dd1ea67.mp4?t=1765469793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以自主进行选择，而你的选择将会影响到那只怪物以及你女儿的命运。你将在游戏过程中不断面对需要谨慎思考的道德困境。简短而充满深意的对话选项让你能够更加深入地了解故事，并发现更多秘密。在此过程中，你将能够与角色进行情感共鸣。  </p>",
